-- Sarkozy May Increase French Value-Added Tax Rate to 21.2%, Le Monde Says
-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 2012-01-28T15:50:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-28/sarkozy-may-increase-french-value-added-tax-rate-to-21-2-le-monde-says.html
French President Nicolas Sarkozy
plans to announce tomorrow the value-added tax will be increased
by 1.6 percentage points to 21.2 percent,  Le Monde  reported on
its website today, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini in Paris at 
